aims-os-math-extras (2.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Carved out of aims-os-math. Holds the full v2.0
    scientific stack: Maxima, full Octave, R tidyverse, multilingual
    TeX Live (English, other, Arabic, publishers, science, XeTeX,
    LuaTeX, bibtex-extra), TeXstudio, GeoGebra, niche Python (mpi4py,
    biopython, skimage, igraph, rpy2, tables, pygments, reportlab),
    and the HDF5 / GMP / MPFR development headers.

